00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:11.620
So, I grew up in a small town in
Massachusetts, the Town of Stowe.

00:01:11.620 --> 00:01:15.410
It was a very small,
boring American town.

00:01:15.410 --> 00:01:19.060 position:56%
