bullying then, they were doing

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:41.740 position:56%
like all the same things they'd done

00:01:41.740 --> 00:01:44.450
to like Puritan kid back
in the 16th century.

00:01:44.450 --> 00:01:46.990
